    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition. It starts and runs, but has some mechanical issues that may require attention over time. The exterior shows visible wear including scratches and possibly minor dents. The interior has signs of use consistent with its age. It is a reasonable option for a buyer who understands they may need to invest in some repairs.",
